{"id": 1414, "genre": 1001, "title": "什么情况下，你会专门给服务人员好评？", "description": "是发自肺腑的觉得服务优秀，“写好评打 9.5 折”的那种不算！（题图来自：林小妖）", "record_count": 4582, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201703221103515r8iZkd9cIJfYelg.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-01-05T03:00:19Z", "options": [{"id": 150784, "content": "我想自己逛的时候，不跟着我叨逼叨，我想寻求帮助の时候，马上出现在我身边，说白了有眼力见！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 891843}, {"id": 152833, "content": "有礼貌！能为我提供一些中肯的建议", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 901367}, {"id": 150786, "content": "长的帅，还超积极主动服务", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 775514}, {"id": 151300, "content": "服务范围超出预期", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 893712}, {"id": 150789, "content": "很耐心地说话讲解", "image": null, "praise_count": 55, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 891852}, {"id": 150791, "content": "保持适当的距离服务，而且真诚不会乱推荐最贵的菜给你点。有眼力见，该加水加水，该干嘛干嘛。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 808640}, {"id": 151047, "content": "帮我解决问题的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 892792}, {"id": 152071, "content": "会引导我走流程，不对我的判断有所干扰，不管客人消费多少都保持礼貌", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 764681}, {"id": 151304, "content": "遵守我国法律法规，产品好，质量过硬，服务到位", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 892523}, {"id": 153865, "content": "非常冷的下雨天 外卖小哥专门下车走到寝室楼下还把保温箱一起抱进来的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 903096}, {"id": 150794, "content": "海底捞", "image": null, "praise_count": 58, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 90238}, {"id": 151818, "content": "客气", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 831901}, {"id": 150795, "content": "能够一眼看出你的真正需求，要什么样子的。要贵的，要便宜的，还是要场面的", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 323625}, {"id": 151563, "content": "态度很礼貌的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 895285}, {"id": 151308, "content": "京东快递员", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 136296}, {"id": 151564, "content": "没有及时接到外卖电话让人家久等", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 891199}, {"id": 150797, "content": "别点了。可以了。够吃了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 719650}, {"id": 151566, "content": "专业并实事求是", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 864759}, {"id": 150799, "content": "什么都替我着想，全心全意的服务", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 887545}, {"id": 153871, "content": "有礼貌，干脆利落，其实只要店里人多的时候别不耐烦就行。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 904812}, {"id": 150800, "content": "跟我说好评就送一份凉粉/xxxxx", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 193260}, {"id": 150802, "content": "热情但不过分亲近，适度适当，\n礼貌周全有眼色。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 820399}, {"id": 151570, "content": "直接帮我给钱的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 895288}, {"id": 150803, "content": "让我自己逛，有问题问她她会热情回答我，答完不跟着我", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 889639}, {"id": 150804, "content": "给顾客留有空间，而不是一直在旁边，看上去像在等，实际上在催", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 891211}, {"id": 150805, "content": "主动想办法帮我省钱，给我有建设性的建议的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 33, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 891918}, {"id": 151829, "content": "态度好", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 824600}, {"id": 158485, "content": "买东西时跟着我，但不要离我太近", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 915859}, {"id": 151318, "content": "真的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 893824}, {"id": 151830, "content": "让我觉得舒服的服务员", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 896851}, {"id": 152598, "content": "冬天给我递上了一片纸巾，让我擦一擦刚进屋时眼镜上起的雾", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 900996}, {"id": 151319, "content": "颜值高！颜值高！颜值高！重要的事情说三遍！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 893833}, {"id": 151575, "content": "诚恳，周到、细心、大家之间能互相尊重。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 840672}, {"id": 152343, "content": "很懂酒", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 597341}, {"id": 162327, "content": "爽快解决你的需求 不做作\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 926182}, {"id": 151576, "content": "所有超出我期望的服务都会好评，例如：住在一个所有快递都不愿意送上门，要我下楼去取，某天一个快递员直接送上来。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 895348}, {"id": 153368, "content": "吃火锅，服务的我都不好意思了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 891474}, {"id": 150809, "content": "真诚与周到 虽然我知道很困难才能遇见一个", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 586732}, {"id": 150810, "content": "服务到位", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 891936}, {"id": 151324, "content": "以他自己的观点来推荐好吃的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 824977}, {"id": 151836, "content": "真心为顾客着想的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 880927}, {"id": 157468, "content": "温情的外卖小哥", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 838788}, {"id": 150813, "content": "海底捞", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 891947}, {"id": 150814, "content": "长得顺眼。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 321342}, {"id": 151582, "content": "有礼貌的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 895391}, {"id": 151838, "content": "专业素养专业服务态度。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 896910}, {"id": 151839, "content": "好看&对我微笑", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 891465}, {"id": 150816, "content": "很贴心的，有时候他（她）给你介绍时的眼神就可以看出", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 889372}, {"id": 151328, "content": "耐心，不会露出不耐烦的脸色", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 806022}, {"id": 150818, "content": "海底捞", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 255265}]}